### Регистрация
POST http://localhost:55234/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user4",
  "passwordHash": "test_hashed_passssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssword",
  "publicKey": "test_public_keytest_public_keytest_public_keytest_public_keytest_public_key",
  "encryptedPrivateKey": "test_encrypted_private_keytest_encrypted_private_keytest_encrypted_private_key"
}

### Вход
POST http://localhost:55234/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user4",
  "passwordHash": "test_hashed_passssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssword"
}

### Публикация сообщения Example API
POST http://localhost:55234/api/v1/example
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3Njk0MzUzNDksInVzZXJJZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ0ZXN0X3VzZXIifQ.CG7y1V4Wkvi4Hbf5Ri43ZWOlY5HIloGEBT34m87U_Ew

{
  "owner": "test_owner",
  "textMessage": "test_textMessage"
}

